Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.29,0:01:35.67,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:91293,95673}{\i1}In order to pay the debt for her father's\Nhospitalization, Nozomi took part in a talent show.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:39.05,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:95673,99051}{\i1}Ironically, she ran into\NEgawa Isao there again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:43.97,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:99051,103973}{\i1}Nozomi singed desperately\Ntrying forget that Egawa is in the jury.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.97,0:01:48.51,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:103973,108519}{\i1}Seeing that like a dog with a bone\NNozomi doesn't lose her passion for singing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:52.89,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:108519,112898}{\i1}Egawa reconsidered his\Ndecision to drive her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:02:02.42,Default,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:117420,122425}{\fad(0,700)}— Episode 16 —\NSinging In The Sunset{NOTE:第16話\\N夕陽にうたえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:16.27,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:132560,136272}Miki-san's so lucky\Nthat she can take lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:19.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:136272,139400}I wish Mr. Egawa started\Nteaching me soon…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:09.39,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:125970,129390}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I feel dead  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:燃えて}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:14.64,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:129390,134645}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I feel dead on the inside    {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:燃え尽きた 今}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:18.39,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:134645,138399}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  It's beyond words  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:傷ついた}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:23.90,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:138399,143904}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  My wings are broken  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:羽を労る}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:28.28,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:143904,148284}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm like a wounded bird  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:仔鳩のように}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:32.32,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:148284,152329}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  The memory of you  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:あなたの思いでを}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.04,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:152329,154040}Let's repeat the last part.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:34.83,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:154040,154832}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:43.96,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:155791,163966}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  The memory of you  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  comes back to haunt me  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:あなたの思いでをやさしく}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:47.13,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:163966,167136}– {\fnArial}♪{\fn}  It slowly decays—\N– Redo.{NOTE:胸にしまうの}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:48.59,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:167136,168596}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:55.10,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:172850,175102}Sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:58.10,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:175102,178105}Sir, what is wrong\Nwith the way I sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.10,0:03:02.86,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:178105,182860}I firmly believe that my skills don't lose\Nto any professional vocalist on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:04.44,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:182860,184445}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.44,0:03:08.36,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:184445,188365}Miki was excellent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:13.24,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:189158,193245}Especially the last part,\Nher technique was so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.24,0:03:16.37,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:193245,196373}She singed so well that\Nit gave me goosebumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:20.50,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:196373,200503}When it comes to your technique,\NI admit there is nothing to complain about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.29,0:03:25.50,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:202296,205508}You can make a few successful discs\Nthe way you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:30.09,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:206509,210096}But this is not enough\Nif you want to become a true singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.09,0:03:32.43,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:210096,212431}The essence of the song\Ncomes from the singer's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:35.22,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:212431,215226}And that soul is something\NI can't feel in your singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:37.31,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:215226,217311}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:40.35,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:217812,220356}I'm sorry.\NI'm being foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.35,0:03:44.15,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:220356,224151}This is the sort of thing\Nthat can't be taught with just words.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:45.31,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:224151,225319}Forget it. Let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:49.03,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:226987,229031}– Sir…\N– Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:51.61,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:229406,231617}Think about your career.\NYour debut is too important.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.61,0:03:55.66,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:231617,235663}If you keep going, you'll make him angry,\Nand that's not something you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.95,0:03:59.04,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:236956,239041}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.09,0:04:17.22,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:255099,257226}He's hard on her, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:21.85,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:257226,261856}She sings so beautifully for once,\Nand he doesn't acknowledge it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:27.36,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:261856,267361}She will soon make her debut,\Nso she cannot afford to fail now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:33.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:268612,273367}I'm so jealous of her. She'll debut soon\Nand Mr. Egawa is working so hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:37.83,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:275828,277830}It's your turn right after.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:43.50,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:277830,283502}There's no way I'm not right. I mean,\Nwhy else would he take you in again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.88,0:04:46.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:285880,286922}You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.92,0:04:49.92,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:286922,289925}You bet I do!\NWell, just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:53.76,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:289925,293762}He'll call you over right after\NMiki-san's lesson is over, trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:293762,295723}That'd be terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:56.84,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:295723,296849}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:57.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:296849,297850}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.31,0:05:00.47,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:299310,300477}It's over. Hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:04.06,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:302521,304064}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:04.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:304064,304565}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:11.40,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:306650,311405}I have an appointment regarding my debut\Nand you're going to accompany me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:14.03,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:311405,314033}We're going to Uchida Productions.\NAnd change those clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:20.66,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:318537,320664}This is nonsense.\NLet's go, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:29.00,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:324835,329006}Master, what about\NNozomi-chan's lessons?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:31.25,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:329006,331258}My lessons for today are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:32.55,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:331258,332551}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.76,0:05:37.51,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:333761,337514}Did I hear you talking about lessons?\NI hope you're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:41.89,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:337514,341894}Do you know what you should be\Nfocused on the most at the moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:43.81,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:341894,343812}Did you forget\Nthat you're my assistant?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.81,0:05:47.73,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:343812,347733}I'm about to make my debut soon.\NIt's a critical time for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:51.11,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:347733,351111}Is it really okay for you\Nto be so carefree?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:53.82,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:351111,353822}But I just wanted\Nto take a few lessons…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:56.20,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:353822,356200}Get it out of your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.20,0:05:58.32,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:356200,358327}Collect our things and we're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:13.71,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:368254,373717}Soul this, soul that. He makes me feel\Nlike I'm some kind of thoughtless animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:17.47,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:373717,377471}Now, now.\NDon't be so mad at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:21.26,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:377471,381267}I know he's hard to deal with,\Nbut you can't act like that in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:23.81,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:381267,383811}Hey, Mom, will you help me\Nwith the advertising campaign?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:26.10,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:383811,386105}Of course I will and you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:29.65,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:386105,389650}Thank you, Mom.\NI can always count on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:34.98,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:389650,394989}Our family will do everything in its power\Nto make sure your career is a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:39.15,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:394989,399159}This practically guarantees my path\Nto stardom. I can't tell you how good it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:41.16,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:399159,401161}You should be happy\Nas well, Nozomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:44.99,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:401161,404999}You won't be an assistant to just a singer,\Nyou'll be an assistant to a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:06:59.63,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:418304,419638}Okay, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:00.88,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:419638,420889}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:03.35,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:420889,423350}Lower your chin a bit.\NThere, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:05.81,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:423350,425811}Right leg a little bit to the back.\NOkay, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.98,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:425811,428981}We'll take a few more.\NDon't move from this spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.11,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:432693,435112}Raise your right arm a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.11,0:07:16.40,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:435112,436405}Chin a bit lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:17.57,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:436405,437573}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:18.82,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:437573,438824}Alright, here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:24.58,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:440492,444580}Inoue-san is now considered\Nto be number one photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.58,0:07:29.58,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:444580,449585}Whoever is photographed by Inoue-san\Nbecomes the talk of the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.62,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:451295,452629}What about the illustrator?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:35.34,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:452629,455341}We've arranged a contract\Nwith Okizu Kōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.34,0:07:38.51,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:455341,458510}Okizu-san's illustrations.\NInoue-san's photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:42.72,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:458510,462723}We could even make artistic posters\Nand sell them for high prices.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:45.14,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:462723,465142}Sounds perfect to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:48.14,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:466602,468145}Alright, let's change the position.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.52,0:07:52.14,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:469521,472149}Come under this spotlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:55.40,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:472900,475402}A moment, please.\NI'm sweating a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:57.27,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:475402,477279}Omine-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:58.82,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:477279,478822}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:00.99,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:478822,480991}I can't believe her.\NWhat kind of assistant is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.99,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:484453,485996}Omine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:07.08,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:485996,487081}Omine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.08,0:08:09.54,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:487081,489541}Hey, can't you hear\Nshe's calling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:10.45,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:489541,490459}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:15.42,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:491752,495422}What are you doing? You're my assistant.\NYou should come immediately when called.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:496799,498926}I can put up with a lot,\Nbut calling me "Omine"…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:22.93,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:499635,502930}W-What's with that look?\NWipe my sweat at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:25.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:504807,505933}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:39.23,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:515359,519238}You're so slow.\NHow long are you going to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:41.11,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:519238,521115}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:43.36,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:521115,523367}Miki-kun, are you ready?\NLet's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:43.95,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:523367,523951}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:09:06.18,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:537131,546181}A new star, Kōda Miki{NOTE:新人香田美紀}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.72,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:547099,549726}What do you think, Maestro?\NShe looks gorgeous, doesn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.93,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:549726,551937}Here, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:13.43,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:551937,553439}Egawa Isao's treasured student,\Nthe master of the song world{NOTE:歌謡界の巨匠\\N江川いさおの秘蔵子！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:13.43,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:552229,553439}"Egawa Isao's treasured student"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:17.44,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:554940,557443}Yes. It has your name on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:25.15,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:560446,565159}I'm only Kōda Miki's teacher.\NI don't remember agreeing to advertise her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.15,0:09:29.66,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:565159,569663}Please don't be so modest.\NIt's only to thank you for your guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:32.29,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:569663,572291}How about dropping this attitude\Njust once, for crying out loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:37.29,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:574042,577296}Listen close, Miki-kun.\NI will say this just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.29,0:09:41.80,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:577296,581800}When you're my student, my responsibilities\Ngo beyond just giving you lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:45.30,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:581800,585304}I'm also fully responsible\Nfor your career.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:49.55,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:586221,589558}If your debut turns to be a fiasco,\Nit's not just you who will get ridiculed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.55,0:09:52.35,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:589558,592352}I become a laughingstock as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:56.19,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:592352,596190}But a man like me cannot afford this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:58.35,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:596190,598358}You're taking this\Ntoo serious, Maestro…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:04.15,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:598358,604156}Now that you put me in this position,\Nget ready for my lessons to get even harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:05.65,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:604156,605657}Even harder?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:10.20,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:607117,610204}I'm ready to respond\Nto your expectations, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:14.37,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:610204,614374}I'll become a singer\Nthat's worthy of your praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:17.79,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:614374,617794}My talent plus your tough lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:21.25,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:617794,621256}We have all the conditions\Nnecessary for me to become a star, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.17,0:10:26.88,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:624176,626887}Alright then, no more idle talk.\NLet's begin with today's lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:28.05,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:626887,628055}Y-Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:46.99,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:643737,646990}{\i1\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I feel dead  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:燃えて}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:52.20,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:646990,652204}{\i1\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I feel dead on the inside    {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:燃え尽きた 今}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:56.04,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:652204,656041}{\i1\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  It's beyond words  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:傷ついた}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:58.96,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:656041,658961}{\fad(0,2000)\i1\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  My wings are broken  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:羽を労る}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:47.32,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:641276,647324}{\i1}My responsibilities go beyond giving lessons.\NI'm also fully responsible for your career.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.32,0:10:51.03,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:647324,651036}{\i1}I'll become a singer\Nthat's worthy of your praise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:54.12,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:651036,654122}{\i1}I'll become a singer.\NI'll become a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.12,0:10:57.41,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:654122,657417}{\fad(0,1000)\i1}I'll become a singer.\NI'll become a singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:10.84,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:666552,670847}I've been thinking, you grew a lot.\NYou have so much patience now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.84,0:11:12.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:670847,672140}Do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.14,0:11:15.72,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:672140,675727}Yes. You know how to hold out\Nwhen things go all wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:19.94,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:675727,679940}You have every right to take singing lessons.\NYou should go talk to Mr. Egawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:21.27,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:679940,681275}Sune-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.27,0:11:23.48,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:681275,683485}I just can't believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:28.24,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:683485,688240}How can he be so excited\Nabout a debut of a girl like Miki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.03,0:11:31.82,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:689032,691827}If he dedicates his time to her,\Nhe must have good reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:38.25,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:691827,698250}But it makes me sick when I think about it.\NIt's just so unfair to you, if you want my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:43.25,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:699501,703255}Alright, I'll go and tell him\Nwhat I think of that hooey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:45.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:704381,705507}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.30,0:11:50.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:709303,710887}Are you okay, Sune-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.72,0:11:54.05,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:711722,714057}What on earth is going on in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.39,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:714057,715392}Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:56.89,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:715392,716893}W-Why can't you take Nozomi-chan—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.89,0:11:58.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:716893,718478}Sune-chan, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:11:59.27,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:718478,719271}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:03.02,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:720522,723025}Mine. Come with me to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:05.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:724651,725902}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:11.65,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:729281,731658}It must be tough for you, Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.36,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:731658,733368}No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:16.37,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:733827,736371}I'll be even stricter from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:17.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:737164,737873}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:23.08,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:738957,743086}First of all, I want you\Nto understand one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:27.04,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:743086,747049}I have no intention to give you\Nany lessons for time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:33.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:752095,753221}Sir…
Comment: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:41.56,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:761563,761563}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.34,0:13:01.26,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:776345,781266}{\i1}I have no intention to give you\Nany lessons for time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:08.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:785228,788607}{\i1}He didn't even want to explain\Nto me the reason for his decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.27,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:788607,791276}{\i1}I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.27,0:13:13.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:791276,793779}{\i1}I looked forward to this so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:18.65,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:793779,798658}{\i1}Sune-chan was right. Why did he\Nbother to take me in again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:21.41,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:798658,801411}{\i1}I don't understand him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.48,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:827145,829481}Alright, cut!\NIt was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:51.19,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:829481,831191}Good work. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:54.61,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:832359,834611}Ah, I'm beat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:56.48,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:834611,836488}Let's take a short break, Miki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:13:59.99,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:838448,839991}Mom, where's Omine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:02.57,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:839991,842577}I thought to get something\Ncool for everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.20,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:842577,845205}so I sent her off to buy\Nsome ice creams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.20,0:14:07.04,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:845205,847040}But she's so slow, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:16.04,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:853004,856049}You sure took your time.\NWhat took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:17.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:856883,857926}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.05,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:857926,860053}Distribute these\Nto everyone at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:21.05,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:860053,861054}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.76,0:14:23.05,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:861763,863056}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.26,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:864558,865267}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:27.10,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:866435,867102}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.85,0:14:29.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:868854,869729}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.72,0:14:30.85,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:869729,870856}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:32.60,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:870856,872607}Thanks for treating us, Miki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:38.94,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:874776,878947}Omine, when you're done,\Ngo clean the edge of the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:39.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:878947,879573}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:42.24,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:880031,882242}Great, that's what I'm\Ntalking about. Nice pose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:43.74,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:882242,883743}Alright, here goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:44.28,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:883743,884286}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.28,0:14:48.54,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:884286,888540}Alright, time for the next pose, but we need\Nsomething to get her up higher…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.67,0:14:54.79,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:893670,894796}Nozomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:55.58,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:894796,895589}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:59.55,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:896756,899551}Come here now, get on all fours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:01.21,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:899551,901219}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:03.63,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:901219,903638}Why are you so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.63,0:15:07.80,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:903638,907809}A good assistant must be ready\Nto do whatever it takes to help her boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.52,0:15:14.35,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:911521,914357}But don't you think\Nthis is a little too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:914357,915317}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:919988,921865}Here, go ahead and\Nuse me as your stool.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:26.62,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:922491,926620}H-Hey, now…\NWait, I'll get something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:27.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:926620,927954}Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:30.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:927954,930874}That's my job, I'm ready to do\Neverything for my mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:35.62,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:932459,935629}{\i1}Good. Looks like you're slowly\Nlearning your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.80,0:15:48.76,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:946806,948767}Okay, here we go. Smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.97,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:948767,949976}Put your arms higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.97,0:15:51.26,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:949976,951269}Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.56,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:951269,952562}Yes, perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:56.19,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:954689,956191}Oh. Nohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:03.24,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:960529,963240}Miki-chan, look over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.24,0:16:05.45,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:963240,965450}Alright, now laugh.\NExcellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:08.07,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:965450,968078}Great. You look super cute. Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.91,0:16:12.20,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:968912,972207}Can you look over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:13.75,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:972207,973750}Yes, exactly like that. Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:17.50,Default,Cameraman,0,0,0,,{TIME:974584,977504}– That's it. Pleasure working with you.\N– Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.88,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:977504,980882}Oh, Mr. Nohara!\NI'm so glad that you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:24.80,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:982300,984803}I'm here as the lyricist\Nfor your debut song.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:26.93,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:984803,986930}That's still very kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:32.60,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:990016,992602}Don't you think that\Nyou're crossing the line?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:36.14,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:992602,996147}Huh? Ah, you're talking about Omine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.27,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:996147,998275}She did it of her own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:42.27,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:998900,1002279}Oh? But in the end, wasn't it you\Nwho ordered her to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.90,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002988,1004906}There's no way she could refuse you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:47.11,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004906,1007117}Admit that you have\Na soft spot for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.11,0:16:49.28,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007117,1009286}I still remember\Nwhat happened at the airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:51.74,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010161,1011746}That's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.08,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011746,1013081}Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:56.33,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1013081,1016334}Look at this, it has your pictures\Nfrom the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:58.67,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016334,1018670}Wow, they look so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.50,0:17:04.84,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019504,1024843}{\i1}For Pete's sake. The photographers went along,\Nbut what would Egawa-san say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:11.01,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027053,1031016}{\i1}There's also the matter\Nof accepting Mine Nozomi back
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:14.06,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031016,1034060}{\i1}but then ignoring her altogether\Nfor Kōda Miki's debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:15.56,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034060,1035562}{\i1}What's going on in his head?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:25.86,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043737,1045864}Where are you going, Mine-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:31.11,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045864,1051119}I have to go to Mr. Egawa's place\Nand get a tape for Miki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:32.87,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051119,1052871}Can you spare a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.87,0:17:34.74,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052871,1054748}There's something I'd like\Nto talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:35.99,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054748,1055999}To me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.04,0:17:39.87,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058043,1059878}This is for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:44.25,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060545,1064257}Yes. It's a song I have\Ncomposed for your debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:48.80,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066551,1068803}Now let's talk a little bit\Nabout the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.80,0:17:50.34,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068803,1070347}A contract?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:52.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070347,1072390}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:56.93,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072390,1076936}This time it'll be with my own studio,\Nwhich I have just founded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:18:01.14,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076936,1081149}I'd like to offer you to become our first\Nsinger ever. What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:04.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081775,1084527}No. I can't leave here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:05.77,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084527,1085779}What makes you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:06.78,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1085779,1086780}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:11.15,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086780,1091159}If you stay at Egawa-san's place, there's\Nno knowing when you get to make your debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:18.79,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093578,1098792}He's the Egawa Isao, I get it.\NBut I'm the number one lyricist, Nohara Jun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:22.37,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098792,1102379}We'll get you your debut right away\Nand make you into a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.37,0:18:27.50,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102379,1107509}My condition is that I'd like you to stop\Nworking as Miki's assistant at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:31.09,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108510,1111096}I hated to see you\Nthe way you were today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:03.42,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142335,1143420}{\i1}Debut…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:05.04,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143420,1145046}{\i1}Debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.04,0:19:06.04,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145046,1146047}{\i1}I could debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:14.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152345,1154389}I'm sorry, but the answer is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:16.97,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155265,1156975}W-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.05,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156975,1158059}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:20.52,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158059,1160520}You could make your debut\Nas a professional singer right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:22.39,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160520,1162397}It's your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:27.40,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164482,1167402}I don't understand\Nyour decision at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:32.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168236,1172949}I think that I'd accept it happily\Nif I didn't meet Mr. Egawa sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.99,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172949,1174993}Egawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:36.11,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174993,1176119}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:40.41,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176119,1180415}I don't know why, but I have a feeling\Nthat he's trying to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:44.87,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181332,1184878}Aren't you overestimating him, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.96,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184878,1186963}Possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.96,0:19:50.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186963,1190467}But I believe in Mr. Egawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:52.09,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190467,1192093}And that's why…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:54.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192093,1194304}At any rate, I have\Nto turn down your offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.30,0:19:55.55,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1194304,1195555}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:58.05,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195555,1198057}Hey! Mine-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:06.14,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201853,1206149}{\i1}Egawa-san…\NYou're a formidable foe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:16.32,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214199,1216326}Looks like you're in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:21.33,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1216326,1221331}Miki-san called to find out if Nozomi-chan's\Narrived to get the tapes, saying she's so slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:29.21,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223792,1229214}I was so furious that I told her that she and you\Njust had a very long and fun discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:32.00,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1229214,1232008}You should be teaching her, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:35.88,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232634,1235887}Why do you give lessons\Nto Miki-san only?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:38.51,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235887,1238515}And watch out for smoking,\NIt's bad for your health!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:52.82,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250318,1252821}{\i1}Nozomi. You want to sing, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.82,0:20:54.53,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252821,1254531}{\i1}I'm sure you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.53,0:20:56.78,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254531,1256783}{\i1}No. I can't imagine\Nyour future any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.78,0:20:58.53,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256783,1258535}{\i1}But true music\Nmust be a cry of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:01.83,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258535,1261830}{\i1}You must express what you had\Nexperienced, what you had felt inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.83,0:21:04.33,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261830,1264332}{\i1}I know you're capable of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:08.75,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266125,1268753}{\i1}I'm sorry, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:11.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268753,1271130}{\i1}Forgive me, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.13,0:21:13.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271130,1273883}{\i1}If I only had accepted that proposal…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:15.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273883,1275927}{\i1}But I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:20.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1275927,1280473}{\i1}Because if I did, I would never be able\Nto look straight in Mr. Egawa's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.43,0:21:25.89,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281432,1285895}{\i1}If you stay at Egawa-san's place, there's\Nno knowing when you get to make your debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:28.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287021,1288606}{\i1}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:31.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1288606,1291401}{\i1}He has his reasons as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1291401,1293945}{\i1}But I don't want to make\Nmy family suffer over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.94,0:21:36.07,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293945,1296072}{\i1}How long do I have to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:41.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300285,1301703}Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:49.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303663,1309294}{\i1}Fanni… You told me once that\NI'm like a canary that forgot its song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.29,0:21:54.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309294,1314132}{\i1}I am now like a bird in a cage\Nthat's craving to sing, but can not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.13,0:21:58.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1314132,1318303}{\i1}Tell me, Fanni.\NHow long do I have to endure?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:05.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320430,1325443}{\i1}How much longer?\NFanni. Tell me, for how long?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:07.97,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326060,1327979}{\i1}Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:09.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327979,1329355}{\i1}Fanni!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:21.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331608,1341951}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Music is my friend  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:歌は私の友達だから}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.95,0:22:30.71,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1341951,1350710}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  When things get hard,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  it stays with me  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:苦しい時も私の見方}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.71,0:22:40.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350710,1360470}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Heard alone it's lonely, but  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:たった一人で淋しいけれど}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:49.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1360470,1369062}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Heard together,  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  it resonates with everyone  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:心の歌をみんなの歌に}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:58.19,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1369062,1378196}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I hope the people  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  downtown can hear it  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:みんなの歌が町いっぱいに}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:06.95,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1378196,1386955}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Let's believe in the tomorrow  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  that will spread someday  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:いつか広がる明日を信じよう}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:37.42,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1351920,1357425}{\i1}Nozomi. To become a real singer,\Nyou must be able to convey your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.42,0:22:40.47,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357425,1360470}{\i1}You still need to\Nrefine your technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:44.72,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1360470,1364724}{\i1}That's why you need training that's even more\Nsevere than what you've been through.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:46.51,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1364724,1366517}{\i1}Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.51,0:22:47.72,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1366517,1367727}{\i1}Endure it!
Comment: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:20.65,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1400652,1400652}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:27.51,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1401928,1407517}{\i1}Kōda Miki's debut party is to be held\Nin summer on a luxury cruise ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:32.23,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1407517,1412230}{\i1}Miki is steadily climbing the stairs\Nto stardom. Compared to her, Nozomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.23,0:23:36.73,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1412230,1416734}{\i1}who is still unable to take any lessons,\Nfeels pathetic and powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.73,0:23:41.99,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1416734,1421990}{\i1}Egawa Isao took Nozomi for a walk by the ocean.\NSuddenly, he tells something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.99,0:23:46.61,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1421990,1426619}{\i1}He orders Nozomi to join\Nclam diggers and dive into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.61,0:23:51.49,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1426619,1431499}{\i1}Please look forward to the next episode:\N"Training By The Sea".
